{
  "stem": "182.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The people were dying just from hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we just couldn't take it any longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And again, Saturday night we gathered by the rabbi who gave us a student, a rabbinical student, or a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he took us to the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He had to follow the river and quietly, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he told us that  as soon as we hear something, we should right away scoot down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We should right away stoop down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we had to cross the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard a wagon from far away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to jump on other side of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a ditch full with water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now there was no time to question, should I or shouldn't I?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all jumped in until the wagon rolled by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now what we did-- it took about two days to get to the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because during the day we had to hide, and we could only travel at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a little food because he knew that if we come to the border, money doesn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if we want somebody's help, we can pay them or the biggest thing we can give them is food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't dare to eat-- my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother and father, they were older, they restrained themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were very hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were told that this is it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the little you can eat, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as we came down at night to continue our trip, two Ukrainian boys or Polish boys ran after us and stopped us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took everything away form us, everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
